  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Red Gem/DST</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><br>\nThe <b>Red Gem</b> is an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> used to craft several <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Magic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magic\">Magical</a> items. It can be used to craft the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire_Staff\" title=\"Fire Staff\">Fire Staff</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Night_Light\" title=\"Night Light\">Night Light</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Life_Giving_Amulet\" title=\"Life Giving Amulet\">Life Giving Amulet</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Purple_Gem\" title=\"Purple Gem\">Purple Gem</a>.\n</p><p>Red Gems can be obtained from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Grave\" title=\"Grave\">Graves</a>, from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tumbleweed\" title=\"Tumbleweed\">Tumbleweeds</a>, as a drop from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Hound\" title=\"Red Hound\">Red Hounds</a>, from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Earthquake\" title=\"Earthquake\">Earthquakes</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Stalagmite\" title=\"Stalagmite\">Stalagmites</a> in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caves\" title=\"Caves\">Caves</a>, and from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ancient_Statue\" title=\"Ancient Statue\">Ancient Statues</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Broken_Clockworks\" title=\"Broken Clockworks\">Broken Clockworks</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ornate_Chest\" title=\"Ornate Chest\">Ornate Chests</a> in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ruins\" title=\"Ruins\">Ruins</a>. \n</p><p>Red Gems have a 0.02% chance to be dropped by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tumbleweed\" title=\"Tumbleweed\">Tumbleweeds</a> and a 5% chance to drop from certain <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Stalagmite\" title=\"Stalagmite\">Stalagmites</a>.\n</p><p>The <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragonfly\" title=\"Dragonfly\">Dragonfly</a> drops 2 Red Gems upon death. Red <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gem_Deer\" title=\"Gem Deer\">Gem Deer</a> also drops one of them if killed or if <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Klaus\" title=\"Klaus\">Klaus</a> is killed. \n</p><p>Red Gems can be crafted by Wilson if he has the &quot;<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Transmute_Gems_I\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Transmute Gems I\">Transmute Gems I</a>&quot; skill.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<p>Red Gems can be inserted into <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winona%27s_G.E.M.erator\" title=\"Winona&#x27;s G.E.M.erator\">Winona&#x27;s G.E.M.erator</a> to power it.\n</p>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Gem\" title=\"Red Gem\"><img alt=\"Red Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Gem.png?a91ebd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem\" title=\"Blue Gem\"><img alt=\"Blue Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Blue_Gem.png?51fe73\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prestihatitator\" title=\"Prestihatitator\"><img alt=\"Prestihatitator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prestihatitator.png/42px-Prestihatitator.png?4c1c7b\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Purple_Gem\" title=\"Purple Gem\"><img alt=\"Purple Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Purple_Gem.png?ca6f08\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Gem\" title=\"Red Gem\"><img alt=\"Red Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Gem.png?a91ebd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\"><img alt=\"Nightmare Fuel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nightmare_Fuel.png?9ed7c9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\"><img alt=\"Spear.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spear.png?63081f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shadow_Manipulator\" title=\"Shadow Manipulator\"><img alt=\"Shadow Manipulator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shadow_Manipulator.png/42px-Shadow_Manipulator.png?576777\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire_Staff\" title=\"Fire Staff\"><img alt=\"Fire Staff.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fire_Staff.png?bd547a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Gem\" title=\"Red Gem\"><img alt=\"Red Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Gem.png?a91ebd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Fuel\" title=\"Nightmare Fuel\"><img alt=\"Nightmare Fuel.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Nightmare_Fuel.png?9ed7c9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></di