might be magic.\n|wanda = It's amazing how many gems you can find just lying around here.\n|choose = woodie\n}}\n\n\nThe '''Red Gem''' is an [[Item]] used to craft several [[Magic]]al items. It can be used to craft the [[Fire Staff]], [[Night Light]], [[Life Giving Amulet]], and [[Purple Gem]].\n\nRed Gems can be obtained from [[Grave]]s, from [[Tumbleweed]]s, as a drop from [[Red Hound]]s, from [[Earthquake]]s and [[Stalagmite]]s in [[Caves]], and from [[Ancient Statue]]s, [[Broken Clockworks]], and [[Ornate Chest]]s in [[Ruins]]. \n\nRed Gems have a 0.02% chance to be dropped by [[Tumbleweed]]s and a 5% chance to drop from certain [[Stalagmite]]s.\n\nThe [[Dragonfly]] drops 2 Red Gems upon death. Red [[Gem Deer]] also drops one of them if killed or if [[Klaus]] is killed. \n\nRed Gems can be crafted by Wilson if he has the \"[[Transmute Gems I]]\" skill.\n\n== {{Pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\nRed Gems can be inserted into [[Winona's G.E.M.erator]] to power it.\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Blue Gem\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Purple Gem\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Spear\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = Fire Staff\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Gold Nugget\n|count3 = 8\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Night Light\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Gold Nugget\n|count3 = 3\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Life Giving Amulet\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = The End is Nigh\n|character = Wickerbottom\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Charcoal\n|count2 = 10\n|item3 = Scales\n|tool = Blueprint (rare)\n|result = Scaled Furnace\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Cratered Moonrock\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|tool = Hand\n|result = Red Moonlens\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Thulecite\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 1\n|result = Firebell\n|character = Wolfgang\n|skill = Dumbbell Developer\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Bio Data\n|count2 = 4\n|tool = Bio Scanalyzer\n|result = Thermal Circuit\n|character = WX-78}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Time Pieces\n|item3 = Marble\n|count3 = 2\n|result = Ageless Watch\n|character = Wanda}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|count1 = 2\n|result = Blue Gem\n|resultcount = 1\n|character = Wilson\n|skill = Transmute Gems I}}\n{{Recipe\n|item5 = Yellow Gem\n|item2 = Orange Gem\n|item3 = Green Gem\n|item4 = Purple Gem\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item6 = Blue Gem\n|result = Iridescent Gem\n|character = Wilson\n|skill = Transmute Gems III}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item3 = Empty Bottle (DST)\n|item2 = Marble\n|count2 = 2\n|result =Soul Jar\n|character = Wortox\n|skill = Soul Jar (Skill)\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|item2 = Thulecite\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count3 = 2\n|item4 = Blue Gem\n|result = Thulecite Slingshot Frame\n|character = Walter\n|skill = Advanced Frames\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Red Gem\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Gears\n|count2 = 1\n|result = Backup Chassis\n|skill = Cold Standby I\n|character = WX-78\n}}\n\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nCzerwone kryształy.png|Old Red Gem texture\nRed Gem emoji from official Klei Discord server.png|Medal red emoji from official Klei Discord server.\nCD redgem.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\nRed Gem 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n\n<tabber>\nResources=\n{{Resources}}\n|-|\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items and Structures on DST}}\n|-|\nFood=\n{{Food}}\n</tabber>\n[[vi:Ngọc Đỏ]]\n[[Category:Naturally Spawning Objects]]\n[[Category:Items]]\n[[Category:Gems]]\n[[Category:Mob Dropped Items]]\n[[Category:Minerals]]\n[[Category:Resources]]\n[[Category:Boss Dropped Items]]\n[[Category:Non-Flammable]]"
